\begin_layout Standard
Harris角点的定义是，如果一点处的Hessian Matrix满足以下条件：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
Det(H)-k*Trace(H)<\epsilon
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
